COPY/PASTE THE CODE FROM YOUR BROWSER INTO THE SUBREDDIT STYLESHEET. 
THEN, GO INTO THE "GREEN-UPVOTE-ACTIVE" FOLDER AND DOWNLOAD THE IMAGE THAT IS THERE. MAKE SURE NOT TO RENAME THE IMAGE AND TO KEEP IT NAMED "GREEN-UPVOTE-ACTIVE".
You will also need to download a cursor image. GO to the "cursor" folder and download the image that is there. MAKE SURE NOT TO RENAME THE IMAGE AND TO KEEP IT NAMED "cursor".


